  "description": "Not-so-simple, not-so-vanilla-like resprites.",
  "body": "![title image](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/2a3f236b04ecc5e4d8c4b905e41003ff5697a5a7.png)\n\nA resource pack for modern versions of Minecraft. \n\n---\n\nThe pack contains my interpretations of ingame items with how I think items should look like, whilst somewhat keeping the vanilla feel.\n\nCurrently, the pack changes the font, title (the _Minecraft_ title in the main menu, typo included!), the main menu panorama and item's textures; blocks and armors will be tweaked later on in the future, along with GUI and HUD elements and miscellaneous stuffs.\n\n---![item showcase](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/ff2e1c3f023342ebd9196249fb1312c3b24934d2.png)",
